  displayName: "K\xF6pek Bal\u0131\u011F\u0131"
  scientificName: Selachimorpha
  habitat: "T\xFCm okyanuslar \u2014 s\u0131\u011F k\u0131y\u0131lardan derin denizlere
    kadar geni\u015F bir alanda ya\u015Far. Baz\u0131 t\xFCrler tatl\u0131 suda da
