  diet: "Karnivor \u2014 bal\u0131klar, m\xFCrekkep bal\u0131klar\u0131, fok, kabuklular
    ve plankton ile beslenir (t\xFCre g\xF6re de\u011Fi\u015Fir)."
  funFact: "K\xF6pek bal\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131n iskeleti tamamen k\u0131k\u0131rdaktan
    olu\u015Fur, hi\xE7 kemikleri yoktur! Ayr\u0131ca di\u015Fleri \xF6m\xFCr boyunca
    yenilenir."
